<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Access Denied - GridScout</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            color-scheme: dark;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top, #1f2937 0%, #111827 50%, #0b1020 100%);
            color: #e5e7eb;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        .card {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 760px;
            background: rgba(17, 24, 39, 0.93);
            border: 1px solid #374151;
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 30px;
            box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
        }

        h1 {
            margin: 0 0 14px;
            color: #f9fafb;
            font-size: 1.9rem;
        }

        p {
            margin: 12px 0;
            color: #d1d5db;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .reason {
            margin-top: 16px;
            border-left: 3px solid #f59e0b;
            background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08);
            padding: 12px 14px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            color: #fcd34d;
        }

        .actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 12px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-top: 24px;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 11px 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            border: 1px solid transparent;
            transition: transform 0.15s ease, opacity 0.15s ease;
        }

        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            opacity: 0.95;
        }

        .button-primary {
            background: #5865f2;
            border-color: #5865f2;
            color: #ffffff;
        }

        .button-secondary {
            background: transparent;
            border-color: #4b5563;
            color: #e5e7eb;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <main class="card">
        <h1>Access Denied</h1>
        <p>
            Your Discord account is authenticated, but GridScout cannot grant access to logs for any shared server.
        </p>
        <p>
            Ask a Discord server administrator to assign you the configured GridScout 
            viewer role, then sign out and sign in again.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you are a Discord server administrator, please ensure all of these 
            steps have been completed:
            <ol>
                <li>Add the GridScout bot to your server using the following link: <a href="https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1473804289532231865" target="_blank">https://discord.com/oauth2/authorize?client_id=1473804289532231865</a></li>
                <li>Use /set-viewer-role in your server to configure the viewer role</li>
                <li>Assign that role to users who should have access to logs here.</li>
                <li>Recommended: use /set-event-channel to configure the event channel for notifications from the bot</li>
            </ol>
        </p>
        <div class="reason"><strong>Details:</strong> <%= reason %></div>

        <div class="actions">
            <a class="button button-primary" href="<%= fix_path('/logout') %>">Sign out</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="<%= fix_path('/auth/discord/login') %>">Login using Discord</a>
            <a class="button button-secondary" href="<%= fix_path('/') %>">Back to Home</a>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
